{"tid":854464,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[新聞] 新一代主機未必叫PS5，但勢在必行","createTime":"2018-10-09T11:20:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-09T13:19:26.000Z","uid":208180,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f9c0a1cb9455b442a1ff50455e35764a01918a46","tid":854464,"uid":208180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T11:20:16.000Z","msg":"在新一期的金融時報中，SONY公司CEO吉田憲一郎簡短地提到了PlayStation下一代主機。<br />\n吉田憲一郎表示，目前來看，我能說的就是，下一代主機硬件勢在必行（necessary）。<br />\n同時對主機是否會叫「PS5」也沒有做出明確的答復。這句話的意思非常模糊，我們暫時不能判斷下一代PlayStation主機目前的狀況，也無法確定新的主機硬件是否會叫做「PS5」，我們唯一能夠確定的是索尼對於新主機有著非常明確的態度。<br />\n金融時報還表示，有傳言索尼將會推出一款能夠連接多種外設的平板設備，以適應流媒體在全球越來越普遍的情況。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/09/191715_5a725298ee8f5ac326a5793f3b9046de.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F09%2F191715_5a725298ee8f5ac326a5793f3b9046de.png&h=f03c30a9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/09/191719_f6fa93b42cfaa077cb97f3480d9d2e07.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F09%2F191719_f6fa93b42cfaa077cb97f3480d9d2e07.png&h=2838bee4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/09/191722_3208e666938726a127dfbd9665badb48.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F09%2F191722_3208e666938726a127dfbd9665badb48.png&h=8f023fc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁叫咩？PS4 Pro Max?  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n買<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔買<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17a92a855f9edde754e88db79f89a371ddd8d887","tid":854464,"uid":5159,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T11:23:11.000Z","msg":"是但叫 PS XX World XS Max Extreme Speed Ultimate GO Pro C